oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This question and answer presentation will deal with a wide variety of subjects including reproductive, castration, herd health, some routine as well as special procedures and my approach to some various clinical presentations. Attendees are encouraged to share their opinions and experiences and we will have adequate time for some questions unrelated to my presentation.
